  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "Lesson 107.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "第107课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "It's Too Small.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "太小了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "Listen to the tape, then answer this question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "听录音，然后回答这个问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "What kind of dress does the lady want?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "这位女士想要什么样的连衣裙？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "Do you like this dress, madam?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "女士，您喜欢这件连衣裙吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "I like the color very much.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我非常喜欢这个颜色。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "It's a lovely dress, but it's too small for me.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "这件连衣裙很漂亮，但对我来说太小了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "What about this one?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "这件怎么样？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "It's a lovely dress.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "这件连衣裙很漂亮。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "It's very smart.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "也很时髦。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "Short skirts are in fashion now.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "现在流行短裙。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "Would you like to try it?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "您想试穿一下吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "All right.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "好吧。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "text": "I'm afraid this green dress is too small for me as well.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "恐怕这件绿色连衣裙对我来说也太小了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "text": "It's smaller than the blue one.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "它比那件蓝色的还小。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "text": "I don't like the color, either.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我也不喜欢这个颜色。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "text": "It doesn't suit me at all.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "它一点也不适合我。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "text": "I think the blue dress is prettier.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我觉得那件蓝色连衣裙更漂亮。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "text": "Could you show me another blue dress?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "您能再给我看一件蓝色连衣裙吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "text": "I want a dress like that one, but it must be my size.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我想要一件那样的，但必须是我的尺码。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "text": "I'm afraid I haven't got a larger dress.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "恐怕我没有更大的连衣裙了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s022",
      "text": "This is the largest dress in the shop.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "这是店里最大的一件。"
      }
    }
  ],
